<div id="banner">
	<h1>Summer Founders</h1>
</div>

<div class="content">
<p>Paul Graham and friends have started a <a title="Summer Founders Program" href="http://paulgraham.com/summerfounder.html">Summer Founders Program</a>; if you have a cool idea they&#8217;ll fund and incorporate a startup for you. All you need to do is spend the summer in Cambridge, MA (they pay living expenses).</p>

<p>If you would like me to work on your startup or else would like to work on mine, <em>sorry the deadline has past. Thanks for your interest.</em></p>

<p class="posted">posted March 18, 2005 03:06 PM (<a class="category" href="cat_technology">Technology</a>) (<a href="#comments">2 comments</a>) <a href="001622" rel="bookmark">#</a></p>
</div>

